courseWork.title: Project Final Deliverable
courseWork.description:
Dear Students,

Please follow these important guidelines for the submission of your project:
Ensure that you submit the complete code of the project. Only one member per group needs to submit the files.
Along with the project, submit the Report (.md file) that includes a detailed description of the project and workflow, along with the description of each module. The report will have a weightage of 30-35% in the evaluation. You can use GitHub to create your report (.md file).
It is important to use charts, diagrams, or tables in the report, as applicable to your project.
In case you have taken any external help or references for your project (dataset, algorithm, library), please cite them appropriately in your report.
Please note that plagiarism will result in zero marks for the project. We will soon be having Project phase 2 evaluations.

courseWork.title: Project Proposal
courseWork.description:
Document (pdf form) will have the following:

1. Title of the project
2. Group members along with Roll#
3. Brief description of the project (What is the project, which issue you are going to solve, why its challenging, why its important etc.)
4. Dataset availability (Source from where you'll get the data)
5. How you will solve the problem (i.e., through which AI technique, and why you've selected that particular technique)
6. Is the code for the project already available?  If so, provide link. And outline why/how you'll be different from the available code
7. Timeline for the project

Note that: This is a firm deadline, pls do not ask for extension.

Thanks,
Asma
